# desc: Snippet for C++11 auto type based on c++-mode/class. 
# Hackish query-replace-regexp to renumber non-mirror fields in the region
# between public and protected (can use N as a field number in the snippet):
# \${[0-9N]*:\([^\$]\) -> ${\,(+ 2 \#):\1
# --
auto ${1:var} = ${2:rhs};
     $0